      "term": "boyarism",
      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "null",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "noun",
          "definition": "The behavior, attitudes, or systems associated with boyars (historical Russian aristocrats) or their influence.",
          "examples": [
            "The novel critiques the old boyarism that defined court life.",
            "Decline of boyarism changed the power structure in the regime."
